bilingual.target: 詹姆斯最终在1787年获得了自由。

bilingual.source: He purchased his own freedom as an adult and joined the Patriot army.
bilingual.target: 他成年后买下了自己的自由并加入了爱国者军队。

bilingual.source: Aung San Suu Kyi has told the world that the people in Myanmar don't have freedom to choose how to live.
bilingual.target: 昂山素季告诉世界缅甸人民没有选择生活方式的自由。

bilingual.source: Over the next few years, James sent many letters to his state government requesting his freedom.
bilingual.target: 在接下来的几年里，詹姆斯向他的州政府寄了许多信件请求自由。

bilingual.source: The statue of liberty is an iconic symbol of freedom.
bilingual.target: 自由雕像是自由的象征。
自由主义强调个人自由和权利。

bilingual.source: She enjoys the flexibility and freedom of freelance.
bilingual.target: 她喜欢自由职业的灵活性和自由。

bilingual.source: The Freeman enjoyed the freedom to travel anywhere.
bilingual.target: 这位自由人享受着随处旅行的自由。

list.abstract: freedom（英[ˈfriːdəm]，美[ˈfriːdəm]），英语单词，名词，意思为自由；摆脱；自由意志。短语搭配有freedom fighter（自由战士），例句为“A sense of freedom driving gives.（驾驶给人的自由感。）” freedom名词类近义词有independence、liberty。

yingyinNormal.en: Free from what? Freedom. Freedom is life's great lie.
yingyinNormal.zh: 牵挂什么？自由，自由是生命中最大的谎言。

yingyinNormal.en: Give Rebecca some space. It's your last birthday of freedom.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你也该让丽贝卡自己待会儿。这可是你最后一个自由的生日了.

yingyinNormal.en: If you help us. I give you my oath. You will have your freedom.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果你可以帮助我们，我向你承诺，你将获得自由。

yingyinNormal.en: Who among you will be the vanguard of democracy, freedom, and discovery?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你们当中谁会成为民主、自由和探索的先锋？

yingyinNormal.en: Between the Autobots who fought for freedom, and the Decepticons who dreamt of tyranny.
yingyinNormal.zh: 为自由而战的汽车人，和梦想独裁的霸天虎之间。

yingyinNormal.en: Find something to blackmail this company and the government. We're gonna get our freedom back.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我会找到把柄威胁他们和政府，再夺回自由。

yingyinNormal.en: That's exactly the kind of spirit with which princess Panchali led the monkeys to freedom.
yingyinNormal.zh: 潘查理公主就是凭这种精神，带领猴子走向自由。

yingyinNormal.en: This is freedom to create, and to do, and to build, as artists, as individuals.
yingyinNormal.zh: 一种有关创造、做事、建造的自由，是一门艺术，是一种独立的精神气质。

yingyinNormal.en: The bright lure of freedom diminishes your life's joy in a mad scramble for power, for identity.
yingyinNormal.zh: 自由的诱惑剥夺了你们生活中的快乐，你们疯狂地追求权势，追求地位。

yingyinNormal.en: Who am I, dad? You're just like me. Yeah? Would you do this? No homework, more freedom.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我是什么样的，爸爸？你就跟我一样。是吗？你会这样做吗？没有作业，更多自由。

yingyinNormal.en: He gets our days. Let's take back our nights. No homework, more freedom. Who's with me?
yingyinNormal.zh: 他占据了我们的白天时间，我们争取回夜晚的时间吧。没有作业，更多自由，谁赞同我？

yingyinNormal.en: I know I'm asking a lot, but the price of freedom is high, it always has been, and it's a price I'm willing to pay.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我知道这很难，但自由的代价是高昂的，一向如此，我愿意付出这个代价。

yingyinNormal.en: Subcontract. I'm one of his suppliers. He offered to buy me out, but I take my freedom where I can find it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他们把工作外包给我。我是他其中一个供应商。他们想买下我，但我更珍惜我的自由。

yingyinNormal.en: Don't start panicking. It's not enough for you to sit around for the rest of your life, but it should buy you your freedom.
yingyinNormal.zh: 先别着急，这笔钱可不够你下半辈子游手好闲，但应该能给你足够的自由。

yingyinNormal.en: It's time to return to a simpler age. One where the powers of freedom can once again operate openly to protect their interests.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是时候回归更简单的时代了，一个可以用自由力量光明正大保护自身权益的时代。

yingyinNormal.en: The people of the world look to us to lead. And we welcome that responsibility. We are heirs to a proud legacy of freedom.
yingyinNormal.zh: 世界人民关注着我们的领导力量，我们欢迎这样的责任心，我们是自由这一引以自豪遗产的继承人。

yingyinNormal.en: Now upon arrival you will be taken in hand by our people so that we might recover our merchandise and you might rediscover the freedom, which you so richly deserve.
yingyinNormal.zh: 落地以后还会有我们的人护送，等我们拿到东西你们就会找回应得的自由。

yingyinNormal.en: The love of family, the joy of good friends, the bonds of community, the freedom we cherish as Americans, the peace and justice we seek in the world.
yingyinNormal.zh: 家人的爱，和好朋友在一起的快乐，社区的团结，我们珍视作为美国人的自由，我们在世界上寻求的和平和公正。

yingyinNormal.en: You may dress like us but you'll never hear the Horns of Freedom when you die, Yondu. And the Colors of Ogord will never lash over your grave.
yingyinNormal.zh: 虽然你打扮得和我们一样，但当你死去的时候，自由的号角不会为你吹响，勇度。掠夺者葬礼的荣光，也不会在你坟墓旁闪耀。

yingyinNormal.en: But the result of ordinary people in every generation doing their part to uphold our founding ideals by taking the blessings of freedom and multiplying them for those who would follow.
yingyinNormal.zh: 而是每一代的普通人做出他们的努力，践行我们的建国理想的结果，带着自由的祝福并将它们赐予更多的后继之人。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence_trans: 规则将阻止宽带提供商在网上挑选赢家和输家，阻止保持自由和创新。

examination_example.sentence: The court, though, may want to allow room for police to cite situations where they are entitled to more <highlight>freedom</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 不过，法院可能希望给警察留出空间，让他们列举自己有权获得更多自由的情况。

examination_example.sentence: Especially significant was his view of <highlight>freedom</highlight>, which, for him, was associated with the rights and responsibilities of the individual.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 特别重要的是他的自由观，对他来说，这与个人的权利和责任有关。

数据源自2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2018-2021年全国重点省市中考试卷，包括听力、阅读、完形、单选、填空、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。
